						<summary>

						<p>Lamp post in front of the Bhōgēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>14th-15th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the cyclic year Pārthiva, Nija-Āshāḍha śu. 5, Thursday (incomplete). States that Śrīgirinātha set up the lamp post for the merit of his parents, Siṅganagauḍa and Nāgasāni.</p>						

